Some genealogies suggest that Narichika was Yoshihira's biological son adopted by Yoshimasa. Another child, "Hōshin," appears in certain sources but is also believed to have been adopted.<ref>''Abe-shi Keizu,'' in ''{{ill|Zoku Gunsho Ruijū|ja|続群書類従|12=draft}}.''</ref>
